    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very sound, starts reliably, and handles smoothly on the road with no known engine or transmission issues. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use, and the exterior paint retains a nice luster, though you may find a few small, typical stone chips or light scratches upon close inspection. It has a solid service history and represents a dependable, high-quality choice for anyone looking for a vehicle that is ready for daily use without immediate maintenance needs.",
